@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(v2)
    tmp = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.75) - v2) * ((v2 + 0.48 * v2 + 0.60) / 0.30))
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.36) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.64)) + (wp.abs(v0 + 0.57) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.86)))
    v1 = wp.cos(0.48)
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v0 + 0.87 + v0 + 0.26)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.68) * (v1 + 0.19 + tmp + 0.22)) / ((tmp + 0.69 + v0 + 0.64) * wp.cos(v2 + 0.86)))
    data[tid] = v0
